'''咖啡酸'''（{{lang-en|'''Caffeic acid'''}}）是一种归属于羟基肉桂酸的有机化合物，同时具有[[苯酚|酚羟基]]和[[丙烯酸|丙烯酸]]两种官能团结构。因为咖啡酸是生物合成植物生物质及其残留物的主要组分之一[[木质素|木质素]]的关键中间体，所以它广泛存在于各种植物中<ref name=Boerjan>{{cite journal|url=http://www.annualreviews.org/doi/10.1146/annurev.arplant.54.031902.134938|doi=10.1146/annurev.arplant.54.031902.134938|title=Ligninbiosynthesis|year=2003|last1=Boerjan|first1=Wout|last2=Ralph|first2=John|last3=Baucher|first3=Marie|journal=Annual Review of Plant Biology|volume=54|pages=519–546|pmid=14503002|access-date=2017-02-05|archive-date=2021-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211204084740/https://www.annualreviews.org/doi/10.1146/annurev.arplant.54.031902.134938|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它可以在热水和[[乙醇|乙醇]]中溶解，冷水中微溶。常温下为黄白色[[结晶|结晶]]体。

==自然中的含量==
自然界中，咖啡酸可以在[[蓝桉|蓝桉]]的树皮中找到<ref>{{Cite journal|pmid=21761864|doi=10.1021/jf201801q|title=Characterization of Phenolic Components in Polar Extracts of Eucalyptus globulus Labill. Bark by High-Performance Liquid Chromatography–Mass Spectrometry|year=2011|last1=Santos|first1=Sónia A. O.|last2=Freire|first2=Carmen S. R.|last3=Domingues|first3=M. Rosário M.|last4=Silvestre|first4=Armando J. D.|last5=Pascoal Neto|first5=Carlos Pascoal|journal=Journal of Agricultural and Food Chemistry|volume=59|issue=17|pages=9386–93}}</ref>，也可以在淡水蕨类[[槐叶苹|槐叶苹]]<ref>{{cite journal|pmid=18177906|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0031942207006462|doi=10.1016/j.phytochem.2007.10.028|title=Phenolic and other constituents of fresh water fern Salvinia molesta|year=2008|last1=Choudhary|
first1=M. Iqbal|last2=Naheed|first2=Nadra|last3=Abbaskhan|first3=Ahmed|last4=Musharraf|first4=Syed Ghulam|last5=Siddiqui|first5=Hina|last6=Atta-Ur-Rahman|journal=Phytochemistry|volume=69|issue=4|pages=1018–23}}</ref>或[[桑黄蘑菇|桑黄蘑菇]]中发现<ref name="pmid18827365">{{cite journal |doi=10.1248/bpb.31.1968 |last1=Lee |first1=Y.-S. |title=Protein glycation inhibitors from the fruiting body of ''Phellinus linteus'' |journal=Biological & Pharmaceutical Bulletin |volume=31 |issue=10 |pages=1968–1972 |date=October 2008 |pmid=18827365 |url=https://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/bpb/31/10/31_10_1968/_article |last2=Kang |first2=Y.-H. |last3=Jung |first3=J.-Y. |last4=Lee |first4=Sanghyun |last5=Ohuchi |first5=Kazuo |last6=Shin |first6=Kuk Hyun |last7=Kang |first7=Il-Jun |last8=Park |first8=Jung Han Yoon |last9=Shin |first9=Hyun-Kyung |last10=Soon |first10=Sung |access-date=2017-02-04 |archive-date=2012-12-19 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20121219063801/http://joi.jlc.jst.go.jp/JST.JSTAGE/bpb/31.1968?from=PubMed |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===食物中的含量===
咖啡酸在[[咖啡|咖啡]]中的含量非常低，仅为0.03毫克/ 100毫升。它是[[摩洛哥坚果油|摩洛哥坚果油]]所含的主要天然酚类之一<ref>{{Cite journal|doi=10.3923/ajft.2007.679.683|url=http://www.scialert.net/abstract/?doi=ajft.2007.679.683|title=Phenols and Polyphenols ''from Argania'' spinosa|year=2007|last1=.|first1=Z. Charrouf|last2=.|first2=D. Guillaume|journal=American Journal of Food Technology|volume=2|issue=7|pages=679|access-date=2017-02-04|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020115229/https://scialert.net/abstract/?doi=ajft.2007.679.683|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在一些草药，特别是百里香、鼠尾草和留兰香中咖啡
酸的含量较高（约20mg/100g）。在[[锡兰肉桂|锡兰肉桂]]和[[八角茴香|八角茴香]]中的含量约22mg/100g。 向日葵种子中的咖啡酸含量较高（8mg/100g），在红葡萄酒存在一定量的咖啡
酸（1.88mg/100ml），苹果酱，杏和李子中也含有咖啡酸（1mg/100g）。 南美州的草药[[巴拉圭冬青|巴拉圭冬青]]中也有相当高含量的咖啡酸（基于薄层色谱密度测定<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://www.hindawi.com/journals/jamc/2013/658596/|doi=10.1155/2013/658596|title=Determination of Flavonoids, Phenolic Acids, and Xanthines in Mate Tea (Ilex paraguariensis St.-Hil.)|journal=|access-date=2017-02-04|archive-date=2019-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190823083436/https://www.hindawi.com/journals/jamc/2013/658596/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[高效液相色谱法|高效液相色谱法]]<ref>{{cite journal|title = Chemical Composition and Antioxidant Activity of Yerba-Mate (Ilex paraguariensis A.St.-Hil., Aquifoliaceae) Extract as Obtained by Spray Drying|journal = Journal of Analytical Methods in Chemistry|url = http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/jf2008343|doi = 10.1021/jf2008343|access-date = 2017-02-04|archive-date = 2019-12-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191202123536/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/jf2008343|dead-url = no}}</ref>测得的含量为150mg /100g）。同时也存在于大麦谷物中<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Quinde-Axtell | first1 = Zory | last2 = Baik | first2 = Byung-Kee | year = 2006 | title = Phenolic Compounds of Barley Grain and Their Implication in Food Product Discoloration | url = http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/jf060974w | journal = J. Agric. Food Chem. | volume = 54 | issue = 26 | pages = 9978–9984 | doi = 10.1021/jf060974w | pmid = 17177530 | access-date = 2017-02-04 | archive-date = 2021-05-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210506033346/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/jf060974w | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==代谢途径==
===生源合成===
咖啡酸的生源合成是从[[绿原酸|绿原酸]]的香豆酸酯（酯化的侧链醇）经[[羟基化|羟基化]]产生的。 这种羟基化过程产生莽草酸的咖啡酸酯，进而转化为绿原酸。 它是阿魏酸，松柏醇和芥子醇的前体，它们是形成木质素的重要结构单元<ref name=Boerjan/>。

许多种植物能产生咖啡酸及其衍生物咖啡酸苯乙醇酯<ref name="pmid11208940"/>。

