===生物转化===
咖啡因O-甲基转移酶是负责将咖啡酸转化为[[阿魏酸|阿魏酸]]的酶。咖啡酸和相关的邻二酚被组织提取物中的邻二酚氧化酶快速氧化<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Pierpoint | first1 = W. S. | year = 1969 | title = ''o''-Quinones formed in plant extracts. Their reactions with amino acids and peptides | url = http://www.biochemj.org/bj/112/bj1120609.htm | journal = Biochem. J. | volume = 112 | issue = | pages = 609–616 | doi=10.1042/bj1120609}}</ref>。

==药理作用==
在体外研究和动物模型中发现咖啡酸具有多种潜在的药理作用，通过氧化机制咖啡酸对人HT-1080纤维肉瘤细胞系中的对癌细胞增殖的抑制作用。<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Rajendra Prasad | first1 = N. | last2 = Karthikeyan | first2 = A. | last3 = Karthikeyan | first3 = S. | last4 = Reddy | first4 = B. V. | date = Mar 2011 | title = Inhibitory effect of caffeic acid on cancer cell proliferation by oxidative mechanism in human HT-1080 fibrosarcoma cell line | url = | journal = Mol Cell Biochem | volume = 349 | issue = 1–2| pages = 11–19 | doi = 10.1007/s11010-010-0655-7 }}</ref>
咖啡酸在体外和活体内都是一种抗氧化剂<ref name="pmid11208940">{{cite journal |last1=Olthof |first1=M. R. |last2=Hollman |first2=P. C. |last3=Katan |first3=M. B. |title=Chlorogenic acid and caffeic acid are absorbed in humans |journal=J. Nutr. |volume=131 |issue=1 |pages=66–71 |date=January 2001 |pmid=11208940 |doi= |url=http://jn.nutrition.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=11208940 |access-date=2017-02-05 |archive-date=2020-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200626055151/https://academic.oup.com/jn |dead-url=no }}</ref>。咖啡酸还显示出免疫调节和抗炎活性，咖啡酸能使黄曲霉毒素产量降低超过95％，优于其他抗氧化剂。研究表明否则触发[[黄曲霉|黄曲霉]]产生[[黃麴毒素|黃麴毒素]]的应激氧化可被咖啡酸阻碍。
对咖啡酸致癌性的研究具有混合的结果<ref name= Hirose>{{cite journal|journal=Carcinogenesis|volume=19|pages=207–212|year=1998|title=Carcinogenicity of antioxidants BHA, caffeic acid, sesamol, 4-methoxyphenol and catechol at low doses, either alone or in combination, and modulation of their effects in a rat medium-term multi-organ carcinogenesis model|first1=M. |last1=Hirose |first2=Y. |last2=Takesada |first3=H. |last3=Tanaka |first4=S. |last4=Tamano |first5=T. |last5=Kato |first6=T. |last6=Shirai |url=http://carcin.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/reprint/19/1/207.pdf|doi=10.1093/carcin/19.1.207|pmid=9472713|issue=1}}</ref>。 一部分研究结果表明它抑制致癌作用，另一部分结果显示咖啡酸有致癌作用<ref name= Hirose/>。对大鼠进行高剂量咖啡酸的口服给药会引起胃乳头状瘤<ref name= Hirose/>。在相同的研究中，高剂量包含咖啡酸的组合抗氧化剂则能显著减少相同种类大鼠[[结肠|结肠]][[肿瘤|肿瘤]]的生长<ref name= Hirose/>。在一些危险物数据表中咖啡酸被列为潜在致癌物，它已被[[国际癌症研究机构|国际癌症研究机构]]列为[[2B类致癌物|2B类致癌物]]（“可能对人类致癌”）<ref>[http://monographs.iarc.fr/ENG/Classification/ClassificationsGroupOrder.pdf Agents Classified by the IARC Monographs] {{Wayback|url=http://monographs.iarc.fr/ENG/Classification/ClassificationsGroupOrder.pdf |date=20111025122327 }}, [[International_Agency_for_Research_on_Cancer|International Agency for Research on Cancer]]</ref>。一些研究数据显示，大鼠肠道中的细菌可能改变咖啡酸[[代谢产物|代谢产物]]的形成<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|volume=69|pages=1413–1415|year=1972|title=Caffeic acid metabolism by gnotobiotic rats and their intestinal bacteria|first1=M. A.|last1=Peppercorn|first2=P.|last2=Goldman|url=http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/abstract/69/6/1413|pmid=4504351|doi=10.1073/pnas.69.6.1413|issue=6|pmc=426714|access-date=2017-02-05|archive-date=2008-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080808143653/http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/abstract/69/6/1413|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |journal=Journal of Nutrition |volume=133 |pages=1853–1859 |date=1 June 2003 |title=Chlorogenic acid bioavailability largely depends on its metabolism by the gut microflora in rats |first1=M.-P. |last1=Gonthier |first2=M.-A. |last2=Verny |first3=C. |last3=Besson |first4=C. |last4=Rémésy |first5=A. |last5=Scalbert |url=http://jn.nutrition.org/cgi/content/full/133/6/1853 |pmid=12771329 |issue=6 |access-date=2017-02-05 |archive-date=2009-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090408055348/http://jn.nutrition.org/cgi/content/full/133/6/1853 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==化学性质==
咖啡酸易于自动氧化。[[谷胱甘肽|谷胱甘肽]]以及[[硫醇|硫醇]]类化合物（例如[[半胱氨酸|半胱氨酸]]，[[巯基乙酸|巯基乙酸]]或甲琉酚）或抗坏血酸对咖啡酸的褐变和消失具有抑制作用<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Cilliers | first1 = Johannes J. L. | last2 = Singleton | first2 = Vernon L. | year = 1990 | title = Caffeic acid autoxidation and the effects of thiols | url = http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/jf00099a002 | journal = J. Agric. Food Chem. | volume = 38 | issue = 9 | pages = 1789–1796 | doi = 10.1021/jf00099a002 | access-date = 2017-02-05 | archive-date = 2019-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191202171421/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/jf00099a002 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，咖啡酸的褐变是由邻二酚被氧化为邻二醌造成的。在酸性条件下用[[高碘酸钠|高碘酸钠]]对咖啡酸进行化学氧化会生成具有呋喃结构的二聚体（2,5-（3'，4'-二羟基苯基）四氢呋喃3,4-二羧酸的异构体）<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Fulcrand | first1 = Hélène | last2 = Cheminat | first2 = Annie | last3 = Brouillard | first3 = Raymond | last4 = Cheynier | first4 = Véronique | year = 1994 | title = Characterization of compounds obtained by chemical oxidation of caffeic acid in acidic conditions | url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0031942200947903?via%3Dihub| journal = Phytochemistry | volume = 35 | issue = 2| pages = 499–505 | doi = 10.1016/S0031-9422(00)94790-3 }}</ref>。使用[[辣根过氧化物酶|辣根过氧化物酶]]/[[过氧化氢|过氧化氢]]的氧化系统能使咖啡酸聚合<ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Xu | first1 = Peng | last2 = Uyama | first2 = Hiroshi | last3 = Whitten | first3 = James E. | last4 = Kobayashi | first4 = Shiro | last5 = Kaplan | first5 = David L. | year = 2005 | title = Peroxidase-Catalyzed in Situ Polymerization of Surface Orientated Caffeic Acid | url = http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja051637r | journal = J. Am. Chem. Soc. | volume = 127 | issue = 33 | pages = 11745–11753 | doi = 10.1021/ja051637r | access-date = 2017-02-05 | archive-date = 2019-11-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191130213000/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja051637r | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==其他用途==
咖啡酸也用于[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]的[[基质辅助激光解吸/电离|基质辅助激光解吸/电离]][[质谱法|质谱]]分析的辅助基质<ref name="pmid2520223">{{cite journal |last1=Beavis |first1=R. C. |last2=Chait |first2=B. T. |title=Cinnamic acid derivatives as matrices for ultraviolet laser desorption mass spectrometry of proteins |journal=Rapid Commun. Mass Spectrom. |volume=3 |issue=12 |pages=432–435 |date=Dec 1989 |pmid=2520223 |doi=10.1002/rcm.1290031207 |url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/rcm.1290031207/full |access-date=2017-02-05 |archive-date=2017-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827092006/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/rcm.1290031207/full |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==同分异构体==
咖啡酸有三个同属于羟基苯丙烯酸的同分异构体，分别是：
*[[伞形酸|伞形酸]]（2,4-二羟基肉桂酸）
*[[2,3-二羟基肉桂酸|2,3-二羟基肉桂酸]]
*[[2,5-二羟基肉桂酸|2,5-二羟基肉桂酸]]

